Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,00:00:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is with this rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,00:00:18.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was bright and sunny just a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,00:00:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. We'll just have to wait out the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,00:00:22.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,00:00:27.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They say "a good and beautiful woman \Nis unconcerned by rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,00:00:29.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, what are you talking about, Koume?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,00:00:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,00:00:33.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It feels really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,00:00:35.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,00:00:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's a good and beautiful... puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,00:00:45.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Crystal Fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,00:00:45.25,Caption2,,0,0,0,,ASTROLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,00:00:45.25,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,00:00:45.25,Caption4,,0,0,0,,DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,00:00:45.25,Caption5,,0,0,0,,FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,00:00:45.25,Caption6,,0,0,0,,TEAR READING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,00:00:45.25,Caption7,,0,0,0,,DREAM FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,00:00:45.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, people lose their way \Nto their fate, or the crossroads of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,00:00:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,as they wander through the maze of their everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,00:00:51.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In those times,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,00:00:54.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,a diviner can present you with an arrow \Npointing to the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,00:01:00.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The magical power that points the way \Nis sometimes panacea, sometimes poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,00:01:04.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,To possess that power, one must be a girl \Nwho has passed her fifteenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,00:01:10.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The girls in this fortune-telling town \Nare sometimes goddesses, sometimes witches.
