Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,00:02:51.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This house is pretty old!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,00:02:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,00:02:55.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like a ghost's gonna come out any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,00:02:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,00:02:58.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,D-don't say that kind of scary stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,00:03:02.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, but seriously, don't you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,00:03:05.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a weird sound mixed in with the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,00:03:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, I was sneezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,00:03:17.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,D-don't freak us out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,00:03:21.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We sure are unlucky to get \Ncaught out in a sudden downpour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,00:03:25.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yes. Everything we did \Nduring our lunch break was for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,00:03:28.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I broke a teacup this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,00:03:29.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just an unlucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,00:03:34.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know, my mirror cracked this morning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,00:03:41.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A-and the strap on my sandal broke today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,00:03:44.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought that could be a sign of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,00:03:46.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about, Chiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,00:03:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,00:03:58.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, don't nibble at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,00:04:01.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,By her current situation, \NI'd say bad luck is drawn to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,00:04:01.50,Subtitle3,,0,0,0,,No, don't nibble at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,00:04:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A bad omen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,00:04:06.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We learned about it in class before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,00:04:09.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,BAD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,00:04:09.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,GOOD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,00:04:09.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A good omen is a sign that good things will happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,00:04:13.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and a bad omen is a sign that bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,00:04:16.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,For example, when your tea stalks \Nstand up straight, that's a good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,00:04:21.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But if you see a black cat on the road, \Nthat's a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,00:04:24.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,BAD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,00:04:24.95,Caption2,,0,0,0,,GOOD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,00:04:26.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The little things in our day-to-day lives \Ncan tell us what the future will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,00:04:29.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,00:04:34.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,BAD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,00:04:34.50,Caption2,,0,0,0,,GOOD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,00:04:34.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Superstition says seeing a spider \Nin the morning is a good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,00:04:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A good omen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,00:04:40.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now that I know something good will happen, \NI'm getting really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,00:04:43.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Even though it looks like \Na horrible thing is happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,00:04:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But what if it's the opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,00:04:46.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,00:04:48.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,00:04:53.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you know something bad is going to happen, \Nwhat should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,00:05:02.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,BAD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,00:05:02.70,Caption2,,0,0,0,,GOOD OMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,00:04:56.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,00:04:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, it's already that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,00:05:02.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll have that be your homework for next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,00:05:04.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, we have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,00:05:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm gonna think about it all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,00:05:12.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's right! She didn't teach us \Nthe one crucial thing: how to deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,00:05:17.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,True. And it's strange for lots of bad omens \Nto appear all in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,00:05:20.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It must mean that something horrible \Nis going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,00:05:21.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,00:05:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,00:05:25.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya, were you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,00:05:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The kitties are so warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,00:05:35.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What kind of horrible thing is going to happen, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,00:05:41.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Maybe this storm is only the beginning, \Nand even more bad things are going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,00:05:47.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Maybe the g-ghosts that live here \Nwill curse us until our dying day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,00:05:50.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If we don't get out of here soon, \Nwe won't make it home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,00:05:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,00:05:53.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That'd be the worst thing that could happen to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,00:05:56.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,00:06:02.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's storming outside, and four people are \Nstuck inside an old, creepy house...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,00:06:03.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,00:06:08.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A sudden serial murder case is about to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,00:06:12.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These bad omens point to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,00:06:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One by one, they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,00:06:17.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The poor, pitiful girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,00:06:21.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What, however, is the truth behind this incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,00:06:23.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The murderer is in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,00:06:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, that only leaves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,00:06:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A fox spirit! So this was your doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,00:06:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll eat you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,00:06:39.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,00:06:45.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiyataro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,00:06:46.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,Note: Parody of the fable of Kintaro the Golden Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,00:06:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, whoa! Whoa there, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,00:06:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, whoa! Whoa there, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,00:06:52.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Why am I the bear? \NWhoa there, whoa! Whoa there, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,00:06:54.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,00:06:56.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be the worst thing ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,00:06:58.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a fox spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,00:07:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And what kind of story was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,00:07:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,00:07:06.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now we're getting thunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,00:07:08.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Nono?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,00:07:10.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,00:07:13.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I found Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,00:07:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,00:07:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,00:07:18.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I-I can't stand thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,00:07:22.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know it's childish, but I'm really scared of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,00:07:24.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,00:07:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're asking me for help, Nono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,00:07:31.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That doesn't happen often. Usually she's stuck to Chiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,00:07:32.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,00:07:36.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...I didn't bring Matsuko-san with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,00:07:39.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you look a little bit like Matsuko-san, Kon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,00:07:42.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I dunno how happy I am to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,00:07:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't cry, Nono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,00:07:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,00:07:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,00:07:52.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I've only read about this in a book, \Nso I don't know if it'll work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,00:07:54.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I'll give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,00:07:56.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,00:08:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An ancient ritual to stop the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,00:08:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,00:08:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the Rainstopping Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,00:08:06.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hyaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,00:08:07.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmblaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,00:08:09.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hngraaar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,00:08:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Forget about stopping it... I think it just got worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,00:08:18.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You tried your best, Kon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,00:08:20.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, I'm sure the gods are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,00:08:23.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,00:08:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, you two, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,00:08:27.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this what it feels like to have little sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,00:08:30.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This "big sister" thing isn't half bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,00:08:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, look, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,00:08:38.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got another sister who's the biggest handful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,00:08:38.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Chiya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,00:08:38.91,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Banner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,00:08:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're soaking wet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,00:08:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How are you having so much fun with this, Chiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,00:08:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're in a horrible emergency situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,00:08:50.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not horrible at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,00:08:51.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,00:08:55.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've waited out the rain in a new place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,00:08:57.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's like an adventure and it's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,00:09:01.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I were alone it might be a little gloomier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,00:09:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...but it's really fun when we're together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,00:09:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,00:09:16.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, we've been looking for \Nbad things that haven't even happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,00:09:21.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Seeing bad omens makes us \Nstart looking for bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,00:09:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's just a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,00:09:30.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're the one who decides \Nif something is good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,00:09:33.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess we figured out the homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,00:09:34.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,00:09:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're really warm when you're so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,00:09:47.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,00:09:48.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,00:09:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,00:09:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's our final form to help you deal with the thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,00:09:55.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,00:09:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,00:10:00.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a flash! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,00:10:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That one was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,00:10:17.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lightning is quite pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,00:10:20.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've never looked at it so closely before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,00:10:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't scared, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,00:10:28.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's weird, but watching it with you \Nmakes it feel like fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,00:10:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's "fireworks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,00:10:33.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. You haven't seen fireworks before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,00:10:39.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So... fireworks are these big circles of fire \Nthat spread out all through the night sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,00:10:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They sound way scarier than thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,00:10:46.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,K..Koume-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,00:10:56.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,00:11:01.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come out, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,00:11:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,00:11:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,00:11:12.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Alright, when summer comes, \Nlet's all go to a fireworks festival together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,00:11:14.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,00:11:16.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay! Fireworks, fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,00:11:18.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can we go see fireworks tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,00:11:20.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like I said, only when summer comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,00:11:22.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, I can't wait that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,00:11:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,00:11:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Meilomancy is one kind of physiological divining,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,00:11:36.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and it can be used to discern the subject's personality \Nand future by the arrangement and shape of their moles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,00:11:42.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Now, I had you memorize all the meanings \Nbehind the locations of moles for the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,00:11:47.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but from these results, \Nsome of you will have to retake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,00:11:51.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kon-chan got a perfect score.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,00:11:52.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A perfect score?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,00:11:54.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Kon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,00:11:57.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-well, of course I'd do well on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,00:12:01.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm an apprentice, and I don't want \Nto bring shame to the Urara name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,00:12:03.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You studied all night for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,00:12:07.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you fail too, Nono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,00:12:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Weren't you up late studying hard, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,00:12:16.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Kon-chan, some people can't remember things \Neven if they study very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,00:12:19.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-her face looks like Matsuko-san's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,00:12:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,00:12:28.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,My Big Sister's a star student who can do anything, \Nbut I'm not good at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,00:12:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Nono, you've got talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,00:12:35.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Matsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,00:12:39.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think that ventriloquism of yours sure is a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,00:12:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, you three will study for the retake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,00:12:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today's lesson will be a self-study period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,00:12:47.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Awwwwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,00:12:57.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Moles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,00:12:52.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can do it! I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,00:12:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,00:12:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you want to study with me, Nono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,00:13:00.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,00:13:02.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll study by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,00:13:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll study by myself... I'll study by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,00:13:10.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,00:13:13.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now even Nina-sensei's looking like Matsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,00:13:14.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,THREE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,00:13:14.41,Caption2,,0,0,0,,SISTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,00:13:19.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,One Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,00:13:19.87,Caption2,,0,0,0,,One Fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,00:13:17.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A mole on the right cheek means they're methodical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,00:13:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A mole on the lower left shoulder means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,00:13:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't remember all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,00:13:25.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,How are you supposed to tell someone's personality \Nfrom where their moles are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,00:13:27.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of different theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,00:13:32.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Long ago, moles were written with the characters \Nfor "mother" and "black", and called "mother's marks."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,00:13:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do they have something to do with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,00:13:38.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One theory says that when a baby is born,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,00:13:44.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,her mother leaves marks on her in a way that writes \Nthe kind of personality she wishes for her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,00:13:45.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,00:13:47.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like symbols of a mother's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,00:13:50.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Another theory says they form \Nfrom waste particles in the mother's womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,00:13:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Her love is garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,00:13:55.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono has a mole right by her eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,00:14:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's see, a mole under the right eye means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,00:14:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"A devilish woman who is popular with the guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,00:14:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A devilish woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,00:14:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,00:14:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm, mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,00:14:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think a mole by the eye definitely feels a little sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,00:14:17.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,DEVILISH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,00:14:17.45,Caption2,,0,0,0,,NONO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,00:14:15.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll be a Madonna who makes \Nall the men cry when you get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,00:14:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,00:14:22.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't really know where my moles are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,00:14:24.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,00:14:26.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll look them up and see what they mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,00:14:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll be a good way to study, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,00:14:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,00:14:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? But it's kind of embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,00:14:32.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,00:14:34.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only way we learn is by practicing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,00:14:37.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you just said you'd help us study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,00:14:40.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,00:14:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-this is to help with your test, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,00:14:53.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, your tummy's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,00:14:55.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And your skin's so white!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,00:14:56.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll be easy to find your moles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,00:14:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright now, lie down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,00:15:00.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,00:15:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,D-don't look so long, make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,00:15:08.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I found one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,00:15:10.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's one here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,00:15:12.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One's here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,00:15:13.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,00:15:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Chiya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,00:15:20.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kon, if you keep getting red, \Nit'll be harder for us to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,00:15:22.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,00:15:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh! That pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,00:15:24.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,00:15:26.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiya! Stop! \NRub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,00:15:27.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That tickles! Chiya! \NRub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,00:15:29.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Stop! \NRub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub, rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,00:15:31.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Chiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,00:15:32.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't touch people THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,00:15:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen your tummy so close before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,00:15:41.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day we met, \NI decided I'd pet it someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,00:15:42.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense, you crazy feral girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,00:15:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,00:15:47.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Chiya! Forget about her tummy, look for moles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,00:15:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're going to fail the test again if you keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,00:15:51.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,00:15:54.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,00:15:55.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,On the back of the knee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,00:15:57.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,00:16:02.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, I made a weird sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,00:16:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,00:16:08.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-why don't we stop things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,00:16:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,00:16:16.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kon, you have two moles \Nright next to each other on the back of your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,00:16:17.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,00:16:21.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Moles on the neck mean the person \Nis serious and responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,00:16:24.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and a little stubborn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,00:16:25.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's so true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,00:16:28.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,00:16:32.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,These two moles have a deeper, \Neven more terrifying meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,00:16:34.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A terrifying meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,00:16:36.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,LONDON MONTHLY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,00:16:36.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,00:16:44.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,LONDON MONTHLY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,00:16:40.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They look like the bite marks \Nof the ancient vampire Count Dracula!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,00:16:43.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That means you're a vampire, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,00:16:44.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I WILL bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,00:16:46.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,00:16:49.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you even want to have a serious study session?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,00:16:50.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon got mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,00:16:54.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You... you even made me do something \Nreally embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,00:16:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not only will I never be the perfect bride,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,00:17:00.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,but being looked at makes me so embarrassed \NI can't even go to the public baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,00:17:02.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're making a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,00:17:04.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And WHOSE fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,00:17:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm through with you, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,00:17:11.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're gonna be way more embarrassed \Nif you leave like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,00:17:13.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You two study!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,00:17:16.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,00:17:20.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Okay, Chiya-chan, let's do \Nwhat Kon-chan said and study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,00:17:21.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,00:17:25.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,00:17:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Saku, out on patrol?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,00:17:31.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't you have class?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,00:17:34.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, things got a little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,00:17:38.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Should I stop in for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,00:17:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,00:17:40.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's our pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,00:17:42.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll accompany you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,00:17:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,00:17:45.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on things while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,00:17:46.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,00:17:47.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So indifferent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,00:17:49.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I love that about her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,00:17:52.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono, you're really fired up today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,00:17:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,00:17:59.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,No, you're a lot more reliable today. \NYou're like Nina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,00:18:03.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-oh, please. I'm not like my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,00:18:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,00:18:06.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,00:18:10.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a mole on your back, Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,00:18:12.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,00:18:18.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,A mole on the shoulder blade means \Nyou're bold and proactive in everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,00:18:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That matches you perfectly, Chiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,00:18:22.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,00:18:25.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,00:18:26.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,00:18:32.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,U-um, my big sister has a mole on her back, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,00:18:34.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,in the same place you do, Chiya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,00:18:43.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why my Big Sister's always \Nbeen bright and happy and popular with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,00:18:48.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've always hidden behind her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,00:18:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, where are you? Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,00:18:55.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,00:18:57.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,00:18:59.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,B-Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,00:19:03.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you sure cry easily, Nono.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,00:19:05.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,00:19:09.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \Nyour big sister Nina will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,00:19:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,00:19:14.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really. So don't cry anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,00:19:19.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, your charming mole is going to be washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,00:19:23.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh... your sister is really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,00:19:26.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,00:19:32.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But lately, I've been feeling more and more \Nthat I can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,00:19:35.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to change, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,00:19:38.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,After meeting all of you \Nand spending every day with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,00:19:42.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I thought how amazing you are, \Neven though you're the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,00:19:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told myself I had to get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,00:19:52.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to study for this test \Nwithout relying on anyone else today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,00:19:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiya-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,00:19:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,00:19:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-why are you undressing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,00:20:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,00:20:03.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,00:20:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,00:20:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today was the first day Nono didn't rely on my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,00:20:15.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So your sister's finally stepping away from you, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,00:20:17.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh, Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,00:20:23.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's just a little... no, it's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,00:20:31.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Because Nono was always behind me, \NI could look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,00:20:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it until it's dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,00:20:43.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,00:20:46.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, might as well draw a bunch of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,00:20:49.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,00:20:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,00:20:54.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,00:20:58.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono, when we first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,00:21:03.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,you were hiding behind Nina-sensei's back, \Nand we didn't notice you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,00:21:08.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad I get to talk with you a lot now, \Nlike we did today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,00:21:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you wanna change, Nono,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,00:21:19.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,then I'll make a little spell \Nso you can become the Nono you wanna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,00:21:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,00:21:30.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't have moles, you can just draw them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,00:21:33.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's simple, but it's a nice little spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,00:21:35.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,00:21:38.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll do a little spell, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,00:21:40.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are any moles \Nthat would make me an unrivaled beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,00:21:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That would go on the right buttock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,00:21:45.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, show us your butt, Koume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,00:21:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nooo, Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,00:21:49.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll draw it on you as thanks for what you did earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,00:21:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll draw one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,00:21:52.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,00:21:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You girls! Could you be a little quiete-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,00:22:06.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,One Day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,00:22:06.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,One Fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,00:22:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C-Captain Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,00:22:11.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if Captain Saku is an adult or a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,00:22:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's draw a moustache on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,00:22:25.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-you girls!
